<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Bloccit</h1>
  <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
  <p>
    <%= link_to "Sign In", new_session_path %> or
    <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Share</h2>
    <p>Information is power! Share all the interesting things you find out there in the wild.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Vote</h2>
    <p>Love a post (or hate it). Vote your piece of mind and add your voice to the group.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Favorite</h2>
    <p>For those posts you want to stay up-to-date on, favorite them and we will email updates. </p>
  </div>
</div>
